---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About · SurviveTheAI" description="What SurviveTheAI is, who it serves, and the editorial stance that guides every post.">
  <main class="bg-white py-14 text-neutral-900 sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl space-y-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <header class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-neutral-900 sm:text-4xl">SurviveTheAI</h1>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-neutral-700 sm:text-xl">
          SurviveTheAI is a field guide for people who feel the AI flood but refuse to drown. We make it practical to protect your work,
          family, and focus while the ground keeps shifting.
        </p>
      </header>

      <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">What we are</p>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-neutral-900">A survival guide</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We publish playbooks, analysis, and checklists to help you navigate the AI transition without gimmicks or hype. Expect clear
            actions, not vague futurism.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Who it’s for</p>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-neutral-900">Workers, parents, builders</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Professionals protecting their careers, parents raising resilient kids, and leaders making choices that affect real people.
            If you need straight talk and practical moves, you’re in the right place.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Editorial stance</p>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-neutral-900">Fear is allowed. Misinformation is not.</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We acknowledge anxiety about AI, but we refuse to publish doom bait or sloppy claims. Every piece is sourced, checked, and open
            to correction.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-3xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm sm:p-8">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-neutral-500">Our promise</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-neutral-900 sm:text-3xl">We keep it human</h2>
          <p class="max-w-4xl text-neutral-700">
            SurviveTheAI exists to help you make better decisions under uncertainty. We do not trade in dark patterns, popups, or manipulative
            funnels. You get signal-rich writing, clear calls to action, and the option to subscribe—nothing else.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
